snippet.title: Tank Squad - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Tank Squad is a tank combat game, where you take control over your tank and lead your squad to victory during World War II tank battles.

Check out the game on Steam, add it to your wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1498130/Tank_Squad/
